data.description: You’ll love this UPGRADED 1ST FLOOR condo with a one car garage IN A PRIME LOCATION! Enjoy your morning cup of coffee on the screened lanai overlooking the landscaped area. The spacious master bedroom features a large walk-in closet and the master bathroom offers dual sinks and a walk-in shower. Other features include a great eat-in kitchen with custom cabinets, granite counters, pantry and breakfast bar, remodeled guest bath with granite and a walk in shower,  hard wired portable generator, 2020 HVAC SYSTEM AND MORE! Unit is just steps from the 9 hole par 3 golf course (no green fees...golf is included in the association fees) PICKLE BALL, community pool, fitness center, tennis courts, kids play area, bocce ball and more...   Fountain Lakes is a gated community perfectly situated WEST of 41 in Estero and  Great location across from Coconut Point. EASY TO SHOW
